{"tid":1402757,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【暴動有前科】1977年，百警衝擊廉署總部打傷調查員","createTime":"2019-08-03T16:55:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T16:55:00.000Z","uid":228995,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"78d5ebc7f2396ccee66ab0b411882f5c70b0a98b","tid":1402757,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:55:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n反對《逃犯條例》的示威者於上周五（21日）包圍灣仔警察總部，要求與警務處處長盧偉聰對話，以及撤回6.12「暴動」定性，時間長達十多小時，有估計指現場曾有逾萬人聚集。圍搗警總期間，有人向圍牆及警方標誌擲蛋及噴漆，又遮擋警方的閉路電視，過程中無人衝入警總辦公室，亦未爆發正面警民衝突。<br />\n<br />\n警總被萬人包圍的場面，令不少網民想起1977年曾有大批警員包圍衝擊廉署總部，當時有警員衝入辦公室毆打廉署人員，令5名人員受傷。事緣本港警隊於七十年代初以前貪污問題嚴重，時任港督麥理浩於1974年成立廉政公署肅貪，令警隊內人人自危，更觸發警廉衝突。衝突事件爆發8天後，麥理浩宣布指定日子前涉貪的警員可獲特赦，雖令廉署士氣一度受挫，但迅速令香港社會回復穩定，並走上廉潔之路。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2946296/org/d958e593e6e20e835673b1e67d3c0c00.jpg/f0Yjbrb0R3bnIwzCTIA4eS4fsEsKZ_3d7UvM7e1LzO0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2946296%2Forg%2Fd958e593e6e20e835673b1e67d3c0c00.jpg%2Ff0Yjbrb0R3bnIwzCTIA4eS4fsEsKZ_3d7UvM7e1LzO0&h=017636c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2946794/org/24d469e62d3828e95b4043b3ad96297b.png/93Q6ASeeQ0mFFAkYPheO4dAuHZqCWRde6K12AOitdgA\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2946794%2Forg%2F24d469e62d3828e95b4043b3ad96297b.png%2F93Q6ASeeQ0mFFAkYPheO4dAuHZqCWRde6K12AOitdgA&h=e3c83ba8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2999313/org/457e8f8c82a7c93cb97261171e0aac3f.jpg/A9ITiZy0NxFxWaQqTFKIrW01n7h7CDjXUQCABVEAgAU\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2999313%2Forg%2F457e8f8c82a7c93cb97261171e0aac3f.jpg%2FA9ITiZy0NxFxWaQqTFKIrW01n7h7CDjXUQCABVEAgAU&h=98bc2211&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港值得多d人知道呢段歷史，最好有人派街"}]}